[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "約300年前遭帝國侵略而毀的聚落", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120041_story/VO_CHR_120041_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "嘿、嘿、嘿，雖然耗費我們不少工夫，但總算把你逼入絕境了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "唔唔唔……區區人類，膽敢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "哼，龍族也不過這點程度嗎。好了，現在是時候將世界從你們這些自大龍族手中解放了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120041_story/VO_CHR_120041_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "竟、竟然出現落雷！？究竟發生什麼──呃啊啊啊啊啊啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0087.wav"], "content": "呵呵，不曉得自大的是哪邊呢。比起這個，你沒事吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "剛才的落雷……你是輝龍吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喔～你知道我的事啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "身為支配雷電的高傲龍族卻迎合人類，協助他們進行醜惡爭鬥……我對此略有耳聞。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我並沒有打算迎合他們喔。只是因為很有趣才就近觀察而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……感謝你救了我。不過，我無法忽視你的做法。現在立刻停止協助人類吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看看這片大地的慘狀。人類的愚蠢，導致流水淤塞、土地腐朽、清風汙穢。這種事絕對不該被原諒！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我憎恨人類……無法原諒……！若你也是龍族就應該明白吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0092.wav"], "content": "嗯～看到帝國那些傢伙，會有這種想法也很自然吧。不過──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "時至今日……人來人往、發達的貿易都市", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──過了300年之後變化還真大啊。沒想到這裡曾是那個全毀的聚落……呵呵，人類果然很有趣呢～", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喂、喂……大事不妙啦！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "街上行人的聲音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120019_story/VO_CHR_120019_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "是、是龍族！有龍族在攻擊都市！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "街上的人們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "該死的人類……可恨，無法原諒……！我不會繼續默不作聲了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "喂喂，突然攻擊都市，到底在想什麼啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0054.wav"], "content": "龍族啊，請平息你的憤怒！究竟發生了什麼事！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我已等了300年。相信伴隨時間經過，人類將會反省自我，取回尊重自然的正直之心……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然而，你們卻絲毫沒變！經過了300年仍然持續著醜惡的爭鬥，令我們龍族痛苦不已！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "我們害你們痛苦不已？等一下，那不是我們，而是帝國吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "什麼帝國還是王國，我才不管你們之間的區別。我是對全體人類感到憤怒啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔，只能應戰了嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "竟然真的等了300年，你實在很規矩呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "朱庇特！？你認識那隻龍族嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "300年前，他在這裡被帝國攻擊時，我曾經出手救過他。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "當時他也像現在這樣，高聲訴說著對人類的憎恨呢。是我勸他冷靜的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我憎恨人類……無法原諒……！若你也是龍族就應該明白吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0092.wav"], "content": "嗯～看到帝國那些傢伙，會有這種想法也很自然吧。不過──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0088.wav"], "content": "──因為現在的人類很愚蠢，所以就要立刻動手，不會稍嫌太早了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……那是，什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "相較龍族，人類根本和嬰兒沒兩樣吧？所以我覺得對他們大度一點也可以啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "有些難以接受呢。無關乎大人小孩，沒道理放任為害者肆意妄為吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這麼說也是呢。那這樣如何？你就當作是給救了你的我一個面子，能不能再給人類一些時間呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想想喔……100年的話太短，但500年又等太久。折衷取300年如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0087.wav"], "content": "300年的時間對我們龍族來說算不了什麼吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "300年……就算等了又如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "經過這麼長的歲月後將會世代交替、時勢更迭，許多事物的存在方式會隨之改變……也說不定。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "真是曖昧的說法呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "因為我也不知道未來的事嘛。但是，正因如此才有趣。至少比現在就摘取嫩芽好啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若那株嫩芽最終開花結果倒無妨，但要是其腐壞並汙染土地……到時我可不輕饒喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "呵呵，就讓我們好好期待300年後吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我接受輝龍的建議等了300年，相信人類改變的可能性。……然而，結果卻是這樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "人類這300年間絲毫沒有改變。依舊殘害自然，折磨我們，並且持續醜惡的爭鬥！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0036.wav"], "content": "不，但那是因為……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我不想聽你們的藉口！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120041_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "可惡，怎麼辦！？那傢伙完全不肯聽啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……嗯～原來如此。嗯，說得也是。你說的確實也有一番道理。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "朱庇特……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "抱歉囉，尤蒂爾。我要站在他這邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "我從現在起，就是你們的敵人了喔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1010.wav"], "content": "你、你說什麼！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110398011, "title": "絲毫沒變的舊識"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "喔哇啊啊！？騙人的吧。他竟然真的攻擊我們！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2054.wav"], "content": "快住手，朱庇特！為什麼要這麼做……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "還記得我們相遇時，你在締結契約前說過的話嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1003.wav"], "content": "我說過的話？那些話和你這麼做的理由究竟有什麼關係！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "呵呵，那就要你自己想囉！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "唔……看來朱庇特那傢伙是認真的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要是讓他們在這裡隨便大鬧，會使都市的損害擴大的。這時候先暫時撤退應該比較好吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "……嗯，蘭薩弗說得沒錯。先暫時撤退，重整態勢吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "朱庇特……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝謝你的協助，輝龍。但這樣好嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "怎麼了？看到我跟他們敵對，讓你有了罪惡感嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若你不在意是無所謂……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "你似乎有什麼誤會，所以我先說清楚。我本來就沒有刻意地跟人類站在同一邊喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "即使變成人類外貌，我也不打算迎合人類。我只是一直在做自己覺得開心的事而已喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……難以理解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "會嗎？在我看來，這是非常簡潔明瞭的行動方針呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不、不好了！帝國軍出現在城外！帝國軍跑來侵略這座都市了！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "鎮上男性的聲音", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "哎呀？聽說帝國軍跑來侵略了耶。一定是看見王子他們從這裡撤退，所以決定把握機會吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "畢竟這裡對帝國而言是重要的地理位置，以戰略上來看應該也會想拿下吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "簡單來說，就是有其他人類跑來破壞這片土地嗎。……愚蠢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那邊的人類，回答我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120019_story/VO_CHR_120019_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "剛、剛才在城裡大鬧的龍族！？噫噫──別過來啊啊啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "簡潔地回答我的問題。前來侵略這片土地的那些人類，現在在哪裡？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……咦？啊、呃嗯……他們在都市的東邊、紮營……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120019_story/VO_CHR_120019_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……我、我得救了……嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的男性", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "都市東方帝國軍營地", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "礙事的王子一行人已經撤退，現在正是拿下那座都市的絕佳機會！絕對要占領那裡！全軍開始前進！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120008_story/VO_CHR_120008_STORY_0056.wav", "vo_chr_120041_story/VO_CHR_120041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "什麼，竟然是龍族！？王子一行人應該從城裡撤退了才對，為什麼會有龍族……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120166_story/VO_CHR_120166_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "嗚哇啊啊啊！？這種傢伙該怎麼對付啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔……別驚慌，各位帝國士兵！區區一隻龍族，不是我們的對手！重整隊型，將其包圍！給他迎頭痛擊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "可惡，你們在磨蹭什麼！加強攻勢！就是現在，給我上！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "你只會在後面出一張嘴嗎？雖然這種人我也不討厭啦。不過──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──實在不怎麼有趣呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "呃啊啊啊啊啊啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120041_story/VO_CHR_120041_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "隊、隊長被幹掉了！？已經不行了，快逃吧！撤退！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120081_01.png", "speakerName": "帝國兵們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……逃走了嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "真意外。你不去追嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我是憎恨愚蠢的人類。話雖如此，但也不認為所有人類都該滅亡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們所該做的──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "那、那個！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你是……剛才那座都市的居民嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是、是的！我看到龍族先生飛向帝國軍的營地，覺得很在意，不曉得你想做什麼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的孩子", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "你從帝國手中保護了我們的都市對吧！雖然外表有點嚇人，但你其實是很善良的龍族對吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的孩子", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……快回都市去吧。並且轉告眾人，若今後不想被捲進無用的爭鬥中，就離開這片土地吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦……啊，好！我知道了！等回去後，就告訴大家。我先走了，真的很謝謝你！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "鎮上的孩子", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "才剛想說你突然開始攻擊都市，這次卻又擊退前來占領都市的帝國……呵呵，你到底想做什麼呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那座都市聚集了過多人類。所以我才對其進行攻擊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，因為那裡是貿易都市嘛。也是這一帶交通跟貿易的中心地，所以才會被帝國盯上……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……也就是說，你其實是為了讓人類不再繼續醜惡的爭鬥，才故意攻擊那座都市的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒錯。只要我破壞那座都市，讓人類不再接近那裡，爭鬥的必要性也會隨之消失吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "人類過度聚集便會帶來不必要的發展，結果招致無用的爭鬥……剛才的戰鬥就是個好例子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要想消除那般無用的爭鬥，光是討伐當前蔓延各處的惡人，只能算治標不治本。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若要根除人類的醜惡爭鬥，只能斷絕人類之間互相交流，並由我們進行更加嚴格地控管！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "……這就是你利用這300年思考得出的答案嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了讓世界保持正確，隔離、管理人類避免邪惡滋生……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這才是讓爭鬥消失於世上，並消除不幸的最佳方法，也是我們所該做的事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……我們，是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，沒錯。所以輝龍，請你協助我。與我一起導正人類吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "……呼。原來如此，我明白了。我終於理解你得出的答案了。在這個前提下，我──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110398012, "title": "雙面的善變者"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，沒錯。所以輝龍，請你協助我。與我一起導正人類吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "……呼。原來如此，我明白了。我終於理解你得出的答案了。在這個前提下，我──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──要拒絕你的邀請。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼。難道你想說我得出的答案有錯嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "這不是對錯的問題。是有趣與否的問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你那乍看之下前後矛盾的行動，背後究竟有怎樣的理由，我原本對這點還滿感興趣的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "「為了讓世界保持正確，　隔離、管理人類避免邪惡滋生。」……啊～啊，說實話，我太失望了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你的想法是在拒絕變化。你的做法無法讓任何事物有所發展……那樣的話，很無聊吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "無聊？你竟然以那般低俗的基準拒絕我的邀請！？你果然很莫名其妙，無法理解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我憎恨汙染世界的人類，無法原諒！所以要進行肅清與裁修以防他們蔓延。這個想法絕對沒錯！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "就說了，不是對錯的問題。真是的，你這300年絲毫沒變耶……唉，無趣的傢伙。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我無法繼續奉陪你這善變的傢伙。那態度與舉止，我將視為與我敵對的表現……做好覺悟了吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你沒事吧，朱庇特！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "謝謝，尤蒂爾。你來得正是時候呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你是輝龍趕走的人類！？怎麼可能，為什麼會出現在這！為什麼要保護輝龍！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "那是因為我相信跟朱庇特的羈絆……因為我信賴他。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "羈絆……信賴……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我很清楚朱庇特絕對不是邪惡的龍族。他不可能會毫無理由地背叛我們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以撤退之後，我一直在思考朱庇特與我們為敵的真實意圖是什麼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "輝龍的真實意圖……意思是你明白了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "嗯。因為朱庇特給了我很清楚的提示啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2054.wav"], "content": "快住手，朱庇特！為什麼要這麼做……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "還記得我們相遇時，你在締結契約前說過的話嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1003.wav"], "content": "我說過的話？那些話和你這麼做的理由究竟有什麼關係！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210004_story/VO_DRG_210004_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "呵呵，那就要你自己想囉！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2085.wav"], "content": "我在跟朱庇特締結契約前，曾說過「導正誤入歧途的龍族　也是王家的責任！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我想起了當時的事，所以才趕來找你們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "好耶，王子。光憑那些對話就能確實理解我的想法……你果然很有趣呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族和人類、彼此心意相通？莫非這就是羈絆……就是信賴嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2008.wav"], "content": "龍族啊，我能理解你的心情。如你所說，相較於龍族，我們或許是很愚蠢的存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但儘管如此，難道真的沒有將所有人類統一管理以外的選項嗎？應該有更多其他可能性不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "其他的、可能性……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2011.wav"], "content": "嗯，沒錯。除了你所想的道路外，一定還存在其他可能性。所以，請讓我來導正你吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "導正我……？區區人類，究竟希望我怎麼做？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族與人類共同邁進的可能性……我希望你能夠見證。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2084.wav"], "content": "所以，你願不願意來我們居住的聖城一趟呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聖城……你是說那裡存在龍族與人類共同邁進的可能性？你以為我會聽信這種蠢話？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你害怕發現自己一心前進的道路其實是錯的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我會害怕？胡扯，你這人類。你們這般卑微存在的蠢話，身為龍族的我豈會畏懼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "既然如此，就跟我去聖城吧。我會在那裡展現給你看龍族與人類共同邁進的可能性的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2030.wav"], "content": "若看過之後你的想法仍然沒變，到時再重新步上你認為正確的道路就好。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……好吧。既然你這麼說，我就稍微配合那些蠢話吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……呵呵呵。好～啦，會變成怎麼樣呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210004_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110398013, "title": "無聊的傢伙"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "這裡就是聖城嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在這裡，有許多人與龍族共同生活。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "只要看過這裡的生活方式，應該能讓你明白人類與龍族，除了你想的之外，還存在其他道路。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "達～～～～令～～～～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "唔哇，慕慕！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "呵呵，達令歡迎回來♪工作很累吧？要先吃飯？先洗澡？還、是、你、要～？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳是……緋龍嗎？究竟為何變成人類的模樣……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯？你誰啊？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2060.wav"], "content": "他是如此如此這般這般……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "嗯～……原來如此。意思就是要讓他看看我跟達令之間火熱甜蜜的羈絆！沒錯吧♪", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2006.wav"], "content": "咦！？呃，我不是那個意思……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "哎喲，不要害羞嘛～♪但這樣的達令我也超、愛、的！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "等一下，慕慕～～！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………這個，就是他想展現給我看的龍族與人類共同邁進的可能性嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，姑且算是其中一種吧。聖城裡還有很多其他的龍族和人類一起生活。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我來幫你帶路吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110021_story/VO_CHR_110021_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "佩羅、奇羅，吃飯的時間到了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110021_02.png", "speakerName": "塞因福蘭德", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120034_story/VO_CHR_120034_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "咪嗚！咪嗚！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120034_01.png", "speakerName": "佩羅＆奇羅", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "別那麼著急。仔細咀嚼，慢慢吃。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110021_02.png", "speakerName": "塞因福蘭德", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120034_story/VO_CHR_120034_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "咪嗚！咪嗚！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120034_01.png", "speakerName": "佩羅＆奇羅", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "好、好可愛……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110357_story/VO_CHR_110357_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "唔哇，可以直接用手餵耶！？真的爆不得了超可愛的啦！！這一定要啪擦下來才行啊～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110357_01.png", "speakerName": "娜汀", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110021_story/VO_CHR_110021_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "唔，好刺眼！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110021_02.png", "speakerName": "塞因福蘭德", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110357_story/VO_CHR_110357_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "欸，我也可以餵嗎？我想把佩羅跟奇羅直接吃我手上東西的畫面啪擦下來～♪", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110357_01.png", "speakerName": "娜汀", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100002_story/VO_CHR_100002_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "什！？太、太狡猾了！娜汀要餵的話，那我也……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100002_01.png", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喂、喂！？妳們冷靜點！不要隨便餵他們吃東西！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110021_02.png", "speakerName": "塞因福蘭德", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120034_story/VO_CHR_120034_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "咪嗚！咪嗚！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120034_01.png", "speakerName": "佩羅＆奇羅", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110263_story/VO_CHR_110263_STORY_0001.wav", "vo_chr_110264_story/VO_CHR_110264_STORY_0004.wav", "vo_chr_110265_story/VO_CHR_110265_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "這樣就完成了──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "三姊妹", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210030_story/VO_DRG_210030_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "非常好！妳們的鍛冶技術正確實地逐漸上升至新的次元！但還早得很，還有需要精進的地方！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210030_01.png", "speakerName": "阿魯庫托斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210030_story/VO_DRG_210030_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "每日的鍛鍊，與腳踏實地累積的經驗終會化為妳們的糧食，將妳們的鍛冶推至未知的領域！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210030_01.png", "speakerName": "阿魯庫托斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是！教練！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "三姊妹", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110255_story/VO_CHR_110255_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "呵呵，我聽見你們的談話了！既然如此就包在我身上吧！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "以我的騎士教官式運動指導來提高各位的鍛冶技術吧！透過鍛鍊你們的肌肉！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110255_01.png", "speakerName": "榭葉拉", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110265_story/VO_CHR_110265_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦，肌肉……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110265_01.png", "speakerName": "露吉娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110255_story/VO_CHR_110255_STORY_0031.wav"], "content": "沒錯。肌肉是一切的基礎！總之，全員先排成一列！那邊那隻熊也是！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110255_01.png", "speakerName": "榭葉拉", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "熊……難不成、妳是說我嗎！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210030_01.png", "speakerName": "阿魯庫托斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110255_story/VO_CHR_110255_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "抬頭挺胸！你們聽好了！以後記得稱呼我為教官！！那麼，馬上開始進行追加特訓吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110255_01.png", "speakerName": "榭葉拉", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "遵、遵命！教官！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210030_01.png", "speakerName": "三姊妹與阿魯庫托斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110255_story/VO_CHR_110255_STORY_0055.wav", "vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "怎麼樣？看過聖城裡人類與龍族的生活之後，有什麼感想？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……嗯。那個人類想展現給我看的龍族與人類共同邁進的可能性，我似乎懂了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看來，我可能被對人類的憎恨所禁錮，導致自己的視野變得狹窄了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我原本認為人類必須受到龍族管理，才能存活於正道上，但事實似乎並非如此。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然現在還無法完全接受，但我認為人類該被管理的這個想法，或許真的錯了吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……那些話，你是認真的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我說過吧？「你說的也有一番道理。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "輝龍……你、在說……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不好、不好啦！不好啦──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "那姆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100007_story/VO_CHR_100007_STORY_0052.wav"], "content": "帝國又發動攻擊了！再這樣下去，附近的聚落會遭殃的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "那姆", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2006.wav"], "content": "妳說什麼！？我知道了，我們馬上去幫助聚落的大家吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "聽說帝國又進攻了喔。那麼，我們也去參觀一下吧？……參觀醜惡的爭鬥。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110398014, "title": "人類與龍族的觀點"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "這是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110021_story/VO_CHR_110021_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "這下就結束了，喝啊啊啊啊啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110021_02.png", "speakerName": "塞因福蘭德", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120041_story/VO_CHR_120041_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "呃啊啊啊啊啊啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0083.wav"], "content": "就是現在，達令！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_2086.wav"], "content": "嗯，一口氣上吧！此刻請給予我龍族之力──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這是……什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯？看不就知道了嗎？是你最討厭的，無用且醜惡的爭鬥啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120081_story/VO_CHR_120081_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔唔唔，繼續這樣下去的話……全軍撤退！重新整頓態勢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "帝國兵隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120035_story/VO_CHR_120035_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "成功了，帝國軍逃走了！是我們的勝利！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "阿爾貝利亞士兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "哎呀呀，已經結束了。比我想像得還快呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "帝國進攻，然後你們將其擊退……這是常有的事嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "對啊。即使是我們龍族，若受到波及也會做出反應吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就算一方不想戰鬥，一旦開始爭鬥便難以脫身。尤蒂爾也不例外。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……人類果然還是無法放棄爭鬥嗎？若是這樣，我在聖城看見的光景，到底是什麼？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我不懂……究竟什麼才是正確的！？人類是能與我們共生的存在嗎？抑或果然，是應受管理的存在？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "呵呵，你不知道答案嗎？剛才明明說過「我似乎懂了」這樣的話呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊……告訴我答案吧，輝龍……正確的道路存在何處……？我、該怎麼做才好……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "那種事，你自己想啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你好不容易開始改變……終於變得比較有趣了，當然得好好享受啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……你究竟、在說什麼？我無法理解你的意思……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "呵呵呵，盡情煩惱吧。等得出答案後我再聽你說吧。再見囉♪", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還是無法原諒人類嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是你啊……的確，我無法原諒人類。憎恨人類的心情並未消失。但……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……我不懂。聽了你的蠢話來到聖城，看過你們的生活之後，我對自身的想法產生了疑問。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "那個，不就代表你的想法改變了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "改變？不對。我確實一度差點接受你們的意見。然而，目睹剛才的醜惡爭鬥後又不懂了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聖城裡的你們與戰場上的你們……究竟哪邊才是真正的人類？這股憎恨該朝向哪裡才好！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "輝龍什麼也沒說就離開了。只說要我盡情煩惱……我實在無法理解他的想法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "試圖理解只是白費力氣喔。因為他就是那種傢伙。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100010_story/VO_CHR_100010_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "輝龍只是一直在做自己覺得開心的事。那傢伙肯定是看著為煩惱所苦的你來取悅自己而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100010_05.png", "speakerName": "慕慕", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為煩惱所苦的我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "恐怕，你在襲擊都市時並沒有迷惘吧。但是，因為和朱庇特交談，讓你產生了迷惘。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "當時朱庇特之所以裝成與我們敵對，會不會是為了和你好好交談呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "交談……的確，那時的我無法傾聽人類所說。敵對者的話語想必難以傳達給我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "我覺得朱庇特一定是希望你能擁有新的觀點。同時，也希望你能改變。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "原來如此……我一直以來都只以自己身為龍族的價值觀在評斷人類。300年來，都只有自己的觀點……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我曾說人類這300年間絲毫沒有改變……但真正沒變的，其實是我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "你要去哪……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還不知道……但是，我很快就會得出答案。得出答案後，到時我會回來告訴你們的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210011_01.png", "speakerName": "龍族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "嗯，我會等著那個時候的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110398_story/VO_CHR_110398_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "呵呵……你會重新得出什麼答案，我非常期待喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但到時候，我會成為你的同伴，還是成為你的敵人，就無法保證了……呵呵呵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110398_01.png", "speakerName": "朱庇特", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110398015, "title": "逐漸改變的事物"}]